{"tid":1535748,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(實用）免費求救App","createTime":"2019-09-03T13:00:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T13:13:39.000Z","uid":299061,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0f6be10973ad5ceaec5289a91c364355e7f912f7","tid":1535748,"uid":299061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T13:00:53.000Z","msg":"實用資訊：（來源自蘋果財經版）<br />\n【創業起義】人人都是美國隊長（尹思哲）<br />\n<br />\n若要自救，科技媒體Unwire報導，美國有Parachute這求救App，現免費供位於香港的用戶登記。它可以在用戶發動求救模式時，自動傳送SMS、電話給指定聯絡人，更可在一鍵立即直播、錄音及實時記錄求救位置。<br />\n<br />\n重點是免費的原因，是一名香港網民去信，要求開發者能免費供港人使用。當香港有累卵之危，但時勢愈亂，我地愈要振作，各自係自己嘅崗位，做返啲自己擅長嘅嘢，那怕是寫一封信，都會有用。<br />\n<br />\n其實，人人都可以是美國隊長，還記得他在Endgame的經典對白嗎？「我們會贏，Whatever it takes，Good Luck。」<br />\n<br />\n尹思哲<br />\n<a href=\"http://linkedin.com/in/wanszezit\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flinkedin.com%2Fin%2Fwanszezit&d=wLht58ApaBOsBOdSjqbSDR68f20TVEdZexmFDfnZHo4%3D&h=a6781f50\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://linkedin.com/in/wanszezit</a> <br />\n<br />\ninvestMAN<br />\nFor People of Style &amp; Substance<br />\n掌握理財智慧 感受生活品味<br />\n<a href=\"http://facebook.com/investMAN.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffacebook.com%2FinvestMAN.hk&d=wLht58ApaBOsBOdSjqbSDR68f20TVEdZexmFDfnZHo4%3D&h=ead97226\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://facebook.com/investMAN.hk</a>"},{"pid":"cc4fc75277998b326f5d6705717b406040ecaaa0","tid":1535748,"uid":290815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T13:01:36.000Z","msg":"其實要突破困局，依家只有「__」依個選項！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1534823\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1534823</a><br />\n<br />\n延伸閱讀：<br />\n香港民權抗爭&mdash;&mdash;五大訴求，缺一不可？我們需要更多！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1530124\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1530124</a>"},{"pid":"ec55b58827f67536ea5306da395b4e60944d8350","tid":1535748,"uid":198856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T13:01:49.000Z","msg":"好似幾好<br />\n推一推